data.value:
This teacher homepage provides statistic, results, and free view for all the records of the students who played in a particular room. Teacher can also add, create, and manage rooms through this form.
This Application are mainly use to evaluate the student's existing learning skills in mathematics. It analyzes and give over view in respond to the potential of each student.
If you want to view all the records of the student in a specific grade level. Navigate to the evaluation panel and search for the student's name and do not forget to choose his/her grade level.
